This directory contains the source for all of the Mark6 components.

common/
    Library files used for different applications.
extern/
	External source dependencies.
disk2vlbi/
    Translation program that converts from raw pcap format into native
    VLBI data format.
mark6/
    Erlang-based control plane (not yet integrated with data plane).
net2disk/
	PF_RING-based data plane for network to disk capture. Still under construction.
    Treats disk packs as JBOD and implements resilient file system.
net2raid/
    Application used during successful 16 Gbps MIT/NASA demonstration.
scancheck/
    Application for checking vdiff frames.
tstmark6/
    Erlang-based mark6 client.
vdif/
    Simple erlang-based VDIF checker.
